Introduction

Soseo, formerly known as SHUUU, is a South Korean singer-songwriter. She was a member of the girl group Unicorn under the stage name Sally until their disbandment in September 2017. In 2018, she announced that she would be changing her stage name into Lily Pink.

In May 2021, she changed her stage name into SHUUU and made her official solo debut with the digital single "Candy."

On May 31, 2022, she changed her stage name again to Soseo.
